<br>
You can clear that castle pretty easy for some nice BP gems, eb item, and the 2 elementals at the doorway are ph for a shimmering sea spirit. I know he can pop anywhere an elemental is but this spot was the best for my group.<br>
<br>
Nice weapon for the slow/agro but doesn't stack with any slows really so the dot doesn't stick (although it does seem to gain agro procing still) 9/19 is a bit low for dps but till you have better this is not a bad weapon.<br>
<br>
